---
// src/components/VideoShowcase.astro
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gray-50 relative overflow-hidden border-y border-gray-200">
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <div>
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-gold/10 border border-brand-gold/20 text-brand-black font-bold text-sm tracking-wider mb-6">
          SEE US IN ACTION
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Equipped to handle <span class="text-brand-gold">any scale of emergency.</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          We don't just talk about rapid response—we deliver. When severe flooding threatens property or critical infrastructure, our specialized tanker units are deployed to drain thousands of gallons of water fast.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Recent Callout</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
                "Attended with our tanker to drain flood water so it doesn't cause damage to the pump house. Job sorted, infrastructure secured."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="quote-trigger cursor-pointer bg-brand-black hover:bg-brand-gold text-white hover:text-brand-black font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-lg flex items-center gap-2 group">
          Require Emergency Pumping?
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="relative bg-white p-3 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)] border border-gray-200 transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
          
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-6 bg-white rounded-b-xl z-20 border-b border-x border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
             <div class="w-12 h-1.5 bg-gray-200 rounded-full"></div>
             <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-gray-200 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] overflow-hidden bg-black relative flex items-center justify-center" style="width: 267px; height: 476px;">
            <iframe 
              src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Freel%2F1232286531910708%2F&show_text=false&width=267&t=0" 
              width="267" 
              height="476" 
              style="border:none;overflow:hidden" 
              scrolling="no" 
              frameborder="0" 
              allowfullscreen="true" 
              allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share">
            </iframe>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>